text: Novoisayevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Novosubayevsky Selsoviet, Nurimanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 9 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 31 km from Krasnaya Gorka, 15 km from Novy Subay. == References == Category:Rural localities in Nurimanovsky District
title: Novoisayevo
